OL,5, Beer sales plunged in the UK during the
OL,6, Covid pandemic as people avoided pubs  
OL,7, and drank wine and spirits at home     
OL,8, instead, industry analysis found.      
OL,10,FPubs, bars and restaurants lost #5.7bn 
OL,11,Fof revenue from beer sales in 2021     
OL,12,Falone, the British Beer and Pub        
OL,13,FAssociation (BBPA) said.               
OL,15,FIt called on the government to cut beer
OL,16,Fduty to help it recover from the       
OL,17,Feffects of the pandemic restrictions.  
OL,19,FThe Treasury said it froze beer duty   
OL,20,Ffor a fourth year saving brewers #900m.
